window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>John Beck is the hero we don't deserve, but he's exactly who we need when the world falls apart.</b></p> <p>When a surprise EMP attack kills the power grid across most of the United States, the nation crumbles - but a hero rises. John Beck makes it his mission to help the weak against the strong in a new, lawless wilderness. All the while, he fights the demons of his past as he searches for the only family he has left.</p> <p><i>Best Laid Plans </i>is book one of The Crusader EMP Post-Apocalyptic Survival Series and is perfect for fans of Franklin Horton, Ryan Schow, Kyla Stone, Jack Hunt, and AR Shaw.</p>"; 
